----------------------------------------------------------------------
> Member Function: Document::Length ;
  $ int Length ()
> Purpose:
  | Returns the length of the document.  This is only valid if the contents of the document are actually available.  If they are not available, the length returned will be 0.
> Calling Context:
  | 
> Return Value:
  | int
> Parameters:
  = No parameters...
